    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                What is staking?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Staking is the process of locking your crypto tokens for a period of time to earn rewards. When you stake YGCT or YGC, you're helping secure the ecosystem and in return, you receive rewards based on the APY of your chosen tier.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                What's the difference between YGCT and YGC staking?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                YGCT is our utility token focused on platform benefits (discounts, cashback, VIP access) with moderate APYs. YGC is our memecoin with higher APYs and fun community perks like exclusive memes and surprise airdrops.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                Can I unstake anytime?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Flexible tier: Yes, unstake anytime. Locked tiers: You must wait until the lock period ends (30, 90, or 180 days). Early unstaking on locked tiers results in penalty fees and forfeited rewards.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                How are rewards calculated?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Rewards = (Your Staked Amount × APY) / 365 days. They accumulate daily and can be claimed or auto-compounded. Example: Stake 1000 YGCT at 50% APY = earn ~1.37 YGCT per day.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                Is staking safe?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Staking involves smart contract risk. While our contracts are designed with security in mind, always stake amounts you're comfortable with. Never stake more than you can afford to lose. We recommend starting with smaller amounts.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
            <div class="faq-question">
                Where do staking rewards come from?
                <span>+</span>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Rewards come from platform fees (swap/bridge commissions), token allocations for staking incentives, and ecosystem growth. Rewards are sustainable as they're tied to platform usage and revenue.
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

