## **PASO 5: SISTEMA BACKEND - OPCIÓN SIMPLE (Google Sheets)**

### **Configuración del Google Sheet de Staking**

**Crea UN SOLO Sheet con múltiples pestañas:**
```
📊 YageCoin_Staking_Master
├── 📄 YGCT_Stakes (pestaña 1)
├── 📄 YGC_Stakes (pestaña 2)
├── 📄 Rewards_History (pestaña 3)
├── 📄 Platform_Stats (pestaña 4)
└── 📄 Whitelist (pestaña 5)
```

---

### **Pestaña 1: YGCT_Stakes**
```
| A          | B               | C            | D        | E      | F             | G           | H           | I          | J                | K              | L        | M             | N              |
|------------|-----------------|--------------|----------|--------|---------------|-------------|-------------|------------|------------------|----------------|----------|---------------|----------------|
| Timestamp  | Wallet Address  | Amount       | Tier     | APY    | Lock Days     | Start Date  | End Date    | Status     | Daily Reward     | Total Earned   | Paid Out | Last Payment  | TX Hash        |
| 2024-10-15 | 0x123...abc     | 1000         | Gold     | 50%    | 90            | 2024-10-15  | 2025-01-13  | Active     | 1.37             | 45.21          | 20.00    | 2024-11-01    | 0xabc...       |
| 2024-10-16 | 0x456...def     | 500          | Flexible | 15%    | 0             | 2024-10-16  | -           | Active     | 0.21             | 6.30           | 6.30     | 2024-11-15    | 0xdef...       |
Fórmulas Automáticas:
excelColumna I (End Date):
=IF(D2="Flexible", "", H2+F2)

Columna J (Daily Reward):
=C2 * (E2/100) / 365

Columna K (Total Earned):
=IF(I2="Active", J2 * (TODAY() - H2), J2 * (I2 - H2))

Columna I (Status - Auto):
=IF(I2="", "Active", IF(TODAY() > I2, "Completed", "Active"))
```

---

### **Pestaña 2: YGC_Stakes**

**Igual que YGCT_Stakes pero para YGC memecoin**

Misma estructura, diferentes tiers (Degen, Moon Chaser, Diamond Hands)

---

### **Pestaña 3: Rewards_History**
```
| A          | B               | C            | D        | E              | F         | G              |
|------------|-----------------|--------------|----------|----------------|-----------|----------------|
| Date       | Wallet Address  | Token        | Amount   | Type           | Status    | TX Hash        |
| 2024-10-20 | 0x123...abc     | YGCT         | 10.50    | Weekly Payout  | Sent      | 0x789...       |
| 2024-10-20 | 0x456...def     | YGCT         | 5.20     | Weekly Payout  | Pending   | -              |
```

