### **Dashboard para Ti (Google Sheets Pestaña):**
```
| Metric                    | This Week | Last Week | Change |
|---------------------------|-----------|-----------|--------|
| New Stakers               | 25        | 18        | +39%   |
| Total Stakers             | 127       | 102       | +25%   |
| TVL (USD)                 | $127,500  | $89,200   | +43%   |
